    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"002 — EV diffusion across states\"\ndate: 2026-06-11\n---\n\n## Question\n\nDo state-level EV adoption curves follow Bass diffusion dynamics, and do the\nfitted innovation (p) / imitation (q) parameters correlate with income,\nurbanization, or charging infrastructure?\n\n## Setup\n\n::: {#f88e5b9d .cell execution_count=1}\n``` {.python .cell-code}\nimport duckdb\nimport plotly.express as px\nfrom complexity_lab.config import settings\nfrom complexity_lab.simulation.diffusion import fit_bass_by_state\n\ncon = duckdb.connect(str(settings.db_path), read_only=True)\nmonth_panel = con.execute(\n    \"SELECT * FROM panel_state_month WHERE state_code <> 'ALL' \"\n    \"ORDER BY state_code, year, month\").df()\n```\n:::\n\n\n## Bass fits per state\n\n::: {#e3dfe992 .cell execution_count=2}\n``` {.python .cell-code}\nfits = fit_bass_by_state(month_panel, value_col=\"ev_regs\", min_total=1000)\nfits = fits[fits.r2 > 0.95]\nfits[[\"p\", \"q\", \"m\", \"r2\", \"peak_time\"]].sort_values(\"q\", ascending=False).head(15).style.format(\"{:.4g}\")\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=2}\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_6f7b2\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"blank level0\" >&nbsp;</th>\n      <th id=\"T_6f7b2_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >p</th>\n      <th id=\"T_6f7b2_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >q</th>\n      <th id=\"T_6f7b2_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >m</th>\n      <th id=\"T_6f7b2_level0_col3\" class=\"col_heading level0 col3\" >r2</th>\n      <th id=\"T_6f7b2_level0_col4\" class=\"col_heading level0 col4\" >peak_time</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"index_name level0\" >state_code</th>\n      <th class=\"blank col0\" >&nbsp;</th>\n      <th class=\"blank col1\" >&nbsp;</th>\n      <th class=\"blank col2\" >&nbsp;</th>\n      <th class=\"blank col3\" >&nbsp;</th>\n      <th class=\"blank col4\" >&nbsp;</th>\n  